<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5> make a case for something • make a federal case out of something</xh5><p> <i>make a case for something</i>—(also: make out a case for something) give good reasons why smth. should be done: You can easily <u>make a case for</u> giving a placebo as being a valid course of treatment.</p><p> <i>make a federal case out of something</i>—(also: make it a federal case) complain too much; exaggerate the importance of smth.: I only spilled my milk. Why <u>make a federal case out of</u> it.</p> </entry>
